name: Toshi
description: I’m getting a new white Shiba Inu puppy in just two weeks, and his name is Toshi. This little legend is already destined for greatness. Don’t even try to tell me he doesn’t deserve a custom-built, luxury pimp doghouse with velvet cushions and a solid gold nameplate. First things I’m snagging with this airdrop are a diamond-studded collar, gold chain, and probably a tiny Lambo for walks. Burned 49% of the supply like a boss. Enjoy.
